  <h2 class="skip">Introduction</h2>
  <div class="indexread">
    <h3><a class="indexlink" title="Dive Into Greasemonkey table of contents" href="toc/">Read now</a></h3>
    <p><cite>Dive Into Greasemonkey</cite> is a book about programming with <a title="Greasemonkey home page" href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/748">Greasemonkey</a>, a Firefox extension for customizing web pages.  <a title="Dive Into Greasemonkey table of contents" href="toc/">Read it online</a> for free.</p>
    <p>Confused already?  Start with <a href="install/what-is-greasemonkey.html">What is Greasemonkey?</a></p>
